            "stanza_text": "Ce bon vieux pont, sous ses trois arches,\nEn a déjà bien vu de l'eau\nPasser verte avec du galop\nOu du rampement dans sa marche."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Il connaît le pas, la démarche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "De l'errant qui porte un ballot,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Du petit berger tout pâlot",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et du mendiant patriarche.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il connaît le pas, la démarche\nDe l'errant qui porte un ballot,\nDu petit berger tout pâlot\nEt du mendiant patriarche."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Au creux de ce profond pays,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Entre ces grands bois recueillis",
