                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Où l'ombre humide a son royaume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au creux de ce profond pays,\nEntre ces grands bois recueillis\nOù l'ombre humide a son royaume,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Le jour, à peine est-il réel !…",
